enum PLCrashReporterError

NSError codes in the Plausible Crash Reporter error domain.

Enumerator:
PLCrashReporterErrorUnknown  An unknown error has occured.

If this code is received, it is a bug, and should be reported.

PLCrashReporterErrorOperatingSystem  An Mach or POSIX operating system error has occured.

The underlying NSError cause may be fetched from the userInfo dictionary using the NSUnderlyingErrorKey key.

PLCrashReporterErrorCrashReportInvalid  The crash report log file is corrupt or invalid.
